<text top="661" left="90" width="69" height="19" font="6"><b>Agenda</b></text>
<text top="703" left="122" width="186" height="14" font="1">The question concerning Haiti</text>
<text top="739" left="153" width="526" height="14" font="1">Report of the Secretary-General on the United Nations Mission in Haiti (S/1995/922)</text>
